tatuadores.descripcion: Marcos Gutierrez, hailing from Argentina, is a tattoo artist specializing in old school style. With a keen eye for vintage aesthetics, Marcos brings classic designs to life with bold lines and vibrant colors. Each tattoo he creates is a timeless piece of art, paying homage to traditional tattooing while adding his own unique flair. If you're seeking a tattoo that captures the essence of old school charm, Marcos is the artist for you.

Hailing from New Jersey, Elina Marsh is a tattoo artist specializing in minimalist style. With a passion for simplicity and elegance, Elina creates designs characterized by clean lines and subtle details. Each tattoo she creates is a personalized work of art, reflecting her clients' identity and desires. If you're looking for a minimalist and meaningful tattoo, Elina is the artist for you.

Hailing from California, Tania Leal is a tattoo artist specializing in old school style. With a passion for vintage aesthetics, Tania brings classic designs to life with bold lines and vibrant colors. Each tattoo she creates is a timeless piece of art, paying homage to traditional tattooing while infusing her own unique style. If you're looking for a tattoo that embodies old school charm, Tania is the artist for you.

Hailing from Madrid, Spain, Nahuel Gonzalez is a tattoo artist specializing in blackout style. With a knack for bold, solid designs, Nahuel brings a contemporary edge to the art of blackout tattoos. Each piece he creates is a striking statement, blending modern aesthetics with traditional tattooing techniques. If you're seeking a bold and distinctive blackout tattoo, Nahuel is the artist to see.

Each piece she creates is a unique statement, blending modern aesthetics with traditional tattooing techniques. If you're looking for a bold and distinctive blackout tattoo, Mia is the artist to see.

Hailing from New Jersey, Morgan Jones is a tattoo artist specializing in blackwork style. With a passion for intricate designs and solid black ink, Morgan brings a bold and distinctive edge to her work. Each tattoo she creates is a unique expression of artistry and individuality, blending contemporary aesthetics with traditional tattooing techniques. If you're seeking a bold and captivating blackwork tattoo, Morgan is the artist to see.
